education program ranked 1st in Texas, 8th in the South and 21st in the nation by Best-Education-Schools.com Teacher education and administration program ranked 3rd in Texas, 21st in the South and 54th in the nation by Best-Education-Schools.com Special education program ranked 1st in Texas, 9th in the South and 57th in the nation by Best-Education-Schools.com Health promotion program ranked 3rd in Texas, 23rd in the South and 65th in the nation by Best-Education-Schools.com Counseling master's program ranked 2nd in Texas as a top value by TopCounselingSchools.org College of Education ranked 4th in Texas and 31st in the South by Best-Education-Schools.com Early childhood studies program ranked 3rd in Texas and 39th in the South by Best-Education-Schools.com Online counseling master's program ranked 43rd in the nation by AccreditedSchoolsOnline.org   Back to UNT rankings Top Required Links Apply now Schedule a tour Get more info Main Menu Home Admissions Academics Student Life About UNT Research Athletics Giving University Links MyUNT EagleConnect Blackboard People & Departments Calendar UNT Map Jobs at UNT Colleges & Schools Specifically for Current Students Faculty & Staff Alumni & Friends Parents & Family Community Emails Graduate Admissions Freshman Admissions Transfer Admissions International Admissions     Find UNT on Google Maps 1155 Union Circle #311277 Denton, Texas 76203-5017   Visitor Information   940-565-2000   800-RELAY TX   Technical Issues Call us Email Us UNT Map Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Electronic Accessibility | Required Links ©2017 University of North Texas 